PostureAlert

A simple app that alerts you when your posture needs fixing.
What it does

Uses your webcam to watch your posture
Alerts you when you're slouching
Works completely on your device (no data sent anywhere)

How to use it

Install requirements:
Copypip install -r requirements.txt

Run the app:
Copypython3 posture_gui.py

How it works
The app uses your camera to track your body position. A machine learning model (Random Forest) analyzes your posture and decides if it's good or bad. When your posture is bad, you'll get an alert after your set timer.

Requirements

Python 3.6+
Webcam